    	<div id="IMG-featured"><img width="600" height="215" src="http://www.batteredjoystick.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/BJCV0002-1.jpg" class="attachment-large wp-post-image" alt="Victorious Link" /></div>
		    <h1 class="post-title">
      8-Bit Mania    </h1>
            <div class="post-info" id="post-info-single">
      <div id="post-author-image">
        <img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/22892eff552e81f7798c015155449690?s=96&amp;d=retro&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-96 photo' height='96' width='96' />      </div>
      <div class="post-credits-and-time">
        <p>By
          <a href="http://www.batteredjoystick.com/author/christina/" title="Posts by Christina Vazquez" rel="author">Christina Vazquez</a><a href="https://plus.google.com/113282953449510264032" rel="author" title="Google Plus Profile for +" plugin="Google Plus Authorship">+</a>          on
          Oct 6, 2013                  </p>
      </div>
      <!-- end .post-credits-and-time -->

      
      
      
